                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  Standard deviation of the mean of cross-",
                "section for nine identical targets bombarded with",
                "'He' ions of the same incident energy and the",
                "random error obtained in atomic absorption",
                "estimation of the arsenic content."
              ]
            }
          ],
